Human coronavirus 229E - discovered in the 1960s - no vaccine
Human coronavirus OC43 - discovered in the 1960s - no vaccine
Severe acute respiratory syndrome conronavirus - discovered, 2002 - no vaccine
Human coronavirus NL63 - discovered, 2004 - no vaccine
Human coronavirus HKU1 - discovered, 2005 - no vaccine
Middle East respiratory syndrome-related coronavirus - discovered, 2012 - no vaccine
Severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 - discovered, 2019


Not a good track record there for developing vaccines for human coronaviruses...
